727324f-b.title: Queens: Main Street - 59th Avenue
727324f-b.text:
Main Street, west side, south fron 59th Avenue (foreground),
showing the area where new housing developments will be erected.
The dwellings under construction in the center background are on
Morace Harding Boulevard, Main Street being on the extrene left
and is a new thoroughfare here.
P. L. Sperr  Anril 19, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
